*   ## **_AEW World Championship Open Challenge: Hangman Adam Page(c) def. Lee Moriarty_**
    

Great match that saw Lee Moriarty get significant offensive on against the world champion in front of his Hometown

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8d056bd3-95f0-48ee-9ae1-074f3b5cfa19/18120.jpg?format=original)

Adam Copeland doesn't know if he'll be back... but at least tells Christian Cage that Cage still does have a family. 🥺🥺🥺

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/68780070-9b6e-4c2f-a766-402e0609787d/processed_18125.jpg?format=original)

FTR is out giving insincere apologies to Beth Phoenix since Adam Copeland and Christian aren't in the building.

Willow Nightengale confronts FTR by herself!! Willow says Beth is an icon. Beth Copeland is the reason women like Willow don't take SHIT from me like FTR.

Willow says FTR can look at the camera and fix their apology right now or get out of this ring.

Cash gets in her face but she slaps him.

Before FTR can assault Willow, JetSPEED comes out for the save and they chase FTR off.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/168e8349-dfe9-46f3-a798-022a77f3750c/18126.jpg?format=original)

MJF says he can't take this anymore. Ever since he lost his World Championship, he hasn't been himself.

He's leaving until he gets himself together but when he's back... He's coming for the World Championship

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5951756c-1191-47f0-b910-b3c54330e85b/processed_18133.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_The Conglomeration def. The Don Callis Family (Okada/Takeshita/Hechicero)_**
    

Post match Kyle Fletcher comes out and says Hangman was right about how he feels after his loss on Saturday. But he can't think of another way to get back on the horse than to take away HOLOGRAM's undefeated streak.

Hologram currently has the longest winning streak in AEW history.

